Procedure ScrollUp; Assembler;
 Asm
  ClD
  Push ds
  Les di, Screen
  Lds si, Screen
  Add si, 160
  Mov cx, 2000-80
  Rep MovSW
  Mov ax, 0
  Mov cx, 80
  Rep StoSW
  Pop ds
 End;
Procedure ScrollDown; Assembler;
 Asm
  StD
  Push ds
  Les di, Screen
  Lds si, Screen
  Add di, 4000
  Add si, 4000-160
  Mov cx, 2000-79
  Rep MovSW
  Mov ax, 0
  Mov cx, 80
  Rep StoSW
  Pop ds
  ClD
 End;
